{"article_id":"kejxExLJDI87K4UQ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Monday defended former national security adviser Michael Flynn ,","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"saying","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"it 's `` very unfair ''","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"he was charged with a crime and Hillary Clinton","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Hillary Diane Rodham ClintonWarren-Sanders fight raises alarm on the left","depth":2},{"id":5,"text":"Poll :","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Trump trails 2020 Democratic contenders in Michigan","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"US company offers free cybersecurity assistance to campaigns","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"MORE was not .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"\" Well , I feel badly for Gen. Flynn , ''","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Trump told reporters .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"`` I feel very badly .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"He ' s led a very strong life . \"","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Trump claimed","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that Clinton , his Democratic opponent in the presidential election last year , lied to the FBI with impunity about her private email server .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"`` I will say this ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Hillary Clinton lied many times to the FBI .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"Nothing happened to her , \"","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"\" Flynn lied","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and they destroyed his life .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"I think","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"it ' s a shame . \"","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"Then-FBI Director James Comey testified before Congress in July 2016","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"that the agency had `` no basis","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"to conclude","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"she lied to the FBI . ''","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"The president 's show of solidarity comes","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"after Flynn pleaded guilty to lying to the FBI about his conversations with Russian officials during the presidential transition .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"The retired Army lieutenant general is cooperating with special counsel Robert Mueller 's probe into Russia 's election interference .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Investigators are looking at","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"whether the Trump campaign cooperated with the Kremlin 's election meddling effort .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Trump spoke at the White House","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"before departing for Utah ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"where he is scheduled to make a speech .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Flynn ' s guilty plea could spell trouble for Trump ' s White House .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"He is the first person","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"who served in the Trump administration","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"to face charges in Mueller ' s probe","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"and could possibly reveal damaging information about other close Trump confidants , or the president himself , to the special counsel .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Trump is responding","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"by trying to undermine the credibility of Mueller and the FBI ' s team of investigators .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"\" After years of Comey , with the phony and dishonest Clinton investigation","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"( and more ) ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"running the FBI ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"its reputation is in Tatters -","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"worst in History !","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"But fear not ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"we will bring it back to greatness , \"","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"the president tweeted on Sunday .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"He also cited a story about a top FBI agent","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"who was moved off the Russia probe","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"after Justice Department investigators found","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"he sent text messages","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"that were critical of the president .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"pare